How to Run

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt


Prepare dataset

Place training and testing images under:

dataset/images/train/<class_names>/
dataset/images/test/<class_names>/


Example:

dataset/images/train/happy/xxx.png
dataset/images/train/sad/yyy.png


Train the model

python train.py


This will save the trained model as emotion_model.keras.

Run the Streamlit app

streamlit run app.py


Use the app

Choose Upload Image to test static images.

Choose Webcam for real-time emotion recognition.
